=head1 DESCRIPTION

A rule for configuring how Amazon Q Business responds when it
encounters a a blocked topic. You can configure a custom message to
inform your end users that they have asked about a restricted topic and
suggest any next steps they should take.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 SystemMessageOverride => Str

The configured custom message displayed to an end user informing them
that they've used a blocked phrase during chat.



